{"tid":178562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Neobux 分享/討論區","createTime":"2017-03-29T15:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T07:59:58.000Z","uid":100804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf8cf9c6b91ff4b700874f9e3d1c7de42756b83","tid":178562,"uid":100804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，依到有冇人有玩開neobux or 其他ptc(paid to click)?自己主要玩開myfreeshare/clixsense，同埋近期新開同neobux 好似既enclix?有冇人討論下 ?<br />\n<strong>唔知咩係neobux?</strong><br />\n2008 成立既網絡公司，係網賺界既先驅，PTC 界既大佬(無咩邊間頂到差唔多10年都仲係度)佢唔係煩膠叫人download or 網賺link，而係點廣告，點一個大約有0.001美金，係，真係好少，但點廣告唔係neobux 既重點，重點係下線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，除左直接用你條link 註冊既下線，仲有租下線(Rented Referral)(解決搵下線既困難)，下線點一個廣告上線會收0.005(下線唔會因此賺少左)，一日平常會有4個，即係1個referral 正常1個每 日賺0.02<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題唔係個個 Referral咁生性，佢幾日唔點你就要回收(recycle)佢，同埋又要諗下幾時續referral 同買新既referral，所以就有千變萬化既策略，但管理一班下線都係樂趣黎既<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.makemoneyonlinea2z.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/how-to-find-neobux-direct-referral-link-click-here.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makemoneyonlinea2z.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fhow-to-find-neobux-direct-referral-link-click-here.jpg&h=ef5f278d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.neobux-info.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/qwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neobux-info.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2Fqwe.png&h=9c33d13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n老老實實，一夜致富馬會幫到你，但neobux要有耐性， 投放既時間係用半年起黎計，我自己希望可以創造被動收入，1日1美元都好，想知道多D既留個明我再講多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果未聽過又想試下可以按下面條link加入，唔駛錢，係升級做黃金會員要90美元1年，但你唔玩返半年，有返250個referral 都係standard memebr 有so.<br />\n下面係我既referral link,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.neobux.com/?rh=6C6B6163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.neobux.com%2F%3Frh%3D6C6B6163&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9157ba11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.neobux.com/?rh=6C6B6163</a><br />\n如果唔鍾意既可以去返neobux 條link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.neobux.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.neobux.com%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=14a84960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.neobux.com/</a> <br />\n<br />\n廷伸閱讀，有興趣可以睇下，台灣人 10938 Refs， ROI : 21% <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.neobux.com/forum/?/23/604277/Refs-10938-Refs-ROI-21/&amp;vl=EFD55E359A65ADD89EF2423A6142BE20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.neobux.com%2Fforum%2F%3F%2F23%2F604277%2FRefs-10938-Refs-ROI-21%2F%26vl%3DEFD55E359A65ADD89EF2423A6142BE20&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f605e7c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.neobux.com/forum/?/23/604277/Refs-10938-Refs-ROI-21/&amp;vl=EFD55E359A65ADD89EF2423A6142BE20</a><br />\n同場咖哩佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.apheros.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/neobux-record.jpg?w=400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.apheros.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F06%2Fneobux-record.jpg%3Fw%3D400&h=9b7afb22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d31a279f49e874e044c8a6dd3c1dfe5c57922ceb","tid":178562,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b2f6246fa36c6c9f885d2fd516906da8db507c","tid":178562,"uid":14304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"想知多啲"},{"pid":"c135ecfa4a13f1d3abc7a5d565a334450c23a554","tid":178562,"uid":100804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50b2f6246fa36c6c9f885d2fd516906da8db507c","tid":178562,"uid":14304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"想